  "title": "Accounts Executive / Senior Account Executive",
  "description": "<p>We are a medium size Accounting and Corporate Secretary firm with an associate Audit firm occupying ½ floor of Odean Towers overseeing the marinas (MBS). We also have an office in Midvalley Southkey, Johor Bahru. Our headcount is more than 30 and we are expanding.</p>\n<p>We are looking for junior and senior account executives to meet our growing business.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To handle external accounting jobs from various industries</li>\n  <li>Responsible for maintaining complete set of accounts</li>\n  <li>Financial management and monthly/quarterly accounting jobs for clients</li>\n  <li>Timely preparation of clients’ year-end accounts and submission of management reports</li>\n  <li>Prepare quarterly GST schedules and be responsible for quarterly GST submission</li>\n  <li>Multi-task and work independently with initiative, whilst maintaining communication on the status of accounting jobs</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates are welcome to apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirement:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or degree in Accountancy, ACCA or Business Studies</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications</li>\n  <li>Good knowledge of QuickBooks and accounting software advantage</li>\n  <li>Good communication, analytical and problem-solving skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to handle deadlines with commitment</li>\n  <li>Hardworking and positive attitude, with the ability to work as a team or individually</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and client relationship skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you possess the above qualities, we would like to hear from you. Career advancement and attractive remuneration are offered to candidates with relevant qualifications and experience. (We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified)</p>",
